@version 0.9.0

  @description
    @p: A module for improving user experience with Hexagon on mobile devices by removing the 200ms delay when clicking whilst maintaining scroll capabilities.

    @p: Including this module will enable the functionality for touch devices which will emit a 'click' event alongside the touchstart/touchend events if the user hasn't scrolled.

    @p: It is generally recommended that you enable this module.

  @api Fast Click

